      "comment": "PRESSURE POINT (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished in the minors last time when third (18.31) at this track making it back to back placings. Solid record here winning three races. Overdue and expected to feature again. PUDDIN' CAKE (1) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 8 lengths sixth (18.47) last time in a TG1-4W at this track over 305m. Has good early burn and suited drawn the inside. Key chance on best form. AUBREY MISS (8) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when third (18.08) in a TG1-4W at this track. Can turn it around this time. AROUND OUTSIDE (7) is worth including.",
